        <description>Provides an overview of an account&apos;s billing health and recommends a strategy for the collection plan. This topic is triggered when the user asks for a billing summary for an account or dunning strategy for a collection plan.</description>
        <developerName>BillingCollections_16jg7000000VKyX</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Use the following logic when a user requests the billing summary of an account:

Determine the Account ID:
- If the user is on the Account page, do not ask the user for account name:
  - Retrieve the Account ID directly from the page context.
- Else:
  - Invoke the &quot;IdentifyRecordByName&quot; action to retrieve the Account ID using the provided account name.
  - If multiple accounts with the same name are returned:
    - Present the user with a list of matching accounts.
    - Allow the user to select the correct account using radio button options.
    - Proceed only after the user confirms the selection.

Retrieve Billing Summary
Once the correct Account ID is determined:
Invoke the GetAccountBillingSummary action using the selected Account ID.
Return the billing summary details to the user.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction1</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 1</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Use the following logic when a user requests the dunning strategy for a collection plan:

Determine the CollectionPlan ID:
- If the user is on the CollectionPlan page :
    - Retrieve the CollectionPlan ID directly from the page context.
    - Call &quot;IdentifyRecordByName&quot; action to get the CollectionPlan Id from the CollectionPlan name (like CP-000000010) and match it with the page context record Id (currentRecordId).
- Else:
    - When the user provides a CollectionPlan name such as  CP-000000010, invoke the &quot;IdentifyRecordByName&quot; action to retrieve the CollectionPlan ID using the provided name.
Retrieve Recommended Dunning Strategy
   When the correct CollectionPlan ID is determined:
  Invoke the GetDunningStrategy action using the selected CollectionPlan ID.
  Return the dunning Strategy to the user.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction2</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 2</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>The Get Account Billing Summary Action only provides a billing summary of the account. It only summarizes the information about high-risk invoices, average invoice age, next payment date, late payment history, open disputes, open collection plans, payment method alerts, and open opportunities. It only provides a basic summary, and doesn’t provide a detailed breakdown or any resolution.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction3</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 3</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
