But, if &quot;High-Risk Invoices&quot; is not explicitly mentioned in the account billing summary, output this clear message to the user: &quot;I could not find information regarding {metric} for {account name}&quot;. Do not state that there are no high-risk invoices in this case. Do not provide the summary as output.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction5</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
